    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Deep Sea Sweep, you play as a small fish who wants to give the seafloor its former beauty back. There are heaps of filthy treasure chests down there! Luckily, your yellow neighbour seems to appreciate them a lot, and can probably help you get rid of them.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Switch between swimming and classic platform movement</strong> by carrying treasures, dropping them on enemies or switches to progress.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068600/extras/aa4d43c02f4af9f28b26478fbda985de.poster.avif?t=1770047002\" width=672 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068600/extras/aa4d43c02f4af9f28b26478fbda985de.webm?t=1770047002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068600/extras/aa4d43c02f4af9f28b26478fbda985de.mp4?t=1770047002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through many <strong>short but challenging</strong> <strong>levels</strong> mixing action and puzzle.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls are easy to pick up, customizable, and allow tight movements.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in tranquil pixel art environments, and meet colorful and cute characters and enemies.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look out for secrets! Find each level's stars to unlock secret harder levels and shortcuts.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself by going for better times in each level.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068600/extras/c21a7d985f46de6a2de6c4395340791a.poster.avif?t=1770047002\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068600/extras/c21a7d985f46de6a2de6c4395340791a.webm?t=1770047002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068600/extras/c21a7d985f46de6a2de6c4395340791a.mp4?t=1770047002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some say deep down at the bottom of the ocean lies a magic pearl that grants wishes... Maybe this would simplify your task. But in the meantime, there's golden trash to take out!</p>",
